11#include "rtc_base/internal/default_socket_server.h"
12
13#include <memory>
14
15#include "rtc_base/socket_server.h"
16
17#if defined(__native_client__)
18#include "rtc_base/null_socket_server.h"
19#else
20#include "rtc_base/physical_socket_server.h"
21#endif
22
23namespace rtc {
24
25std::unique_ptr<SocketServer> CreateDefaultSocketServer() {
26#if defined(__native_client__)
27 return std::unique_ptr<SocketServer>(new rtc::NullSocketServer);
28#else
29 return std::unique_ptr<SocketServer>(new rtc::PhysicalSocketServer);
30#endif
31}
32
33} // namespace rtc
